user.biography:
A game about placing blocks and going on adventures. Create! Explore! Survive! Here’s how you do it!
ESRB Rating: Everyone 10+ with Fantasy Violence

node.text:
We know, those amethyst geodes look like they formed through ages of mineral deposition, but they actually emerged from the hands of a talented team of artists and developers! 

Back when Caves & Cliffs was first taking shape, concept artist @mariana.salimena made these beautiful explorations of what underground crystals might look like:

node.text: Gather, gather, all together! In just 4 short days, you’ll have more blocks than ever to build a welcoming home for your dearest of friends – animal or otherwise!

The ever-hungry axolotl will be your most loyal companion, so long as you tempt it with a mouth-watering bucket of tropical fish. Write that down, would-be adventurers: tropical fish. No cod; no salmon – and certainly no pufferfish.

To boop someone from a high place
